
Virtual Network Layers
======================

Build:

- Clone vnl
  > git clone https://github.com/madMAx43v3r/virtual-network-layers.git
  - NOTE: currently the development branch is required
  > git checkout devel

- Clone vni
  > git clone https://github.com/madMAx43v3r/virtual-network-interface.git
   
- Build vni
  > cd <vni-dir>
  > mkdir build
  > cd build
  > cmake ../codegen/cpp
  > make
   
- Build vnl libraries
  > cd <vnl-dir>
  > mkdir build
  - Generate sources
    > <vni-dir>/build/vnicppcodegen interface
   > cd build
   > cmake ../